{
  "_comment": [
    "root_sink live histograms for eliadeSN01 (1x V1730SB DPP-PSD, 16 ch).",
    "hit scope only (energy / energy_short / channel / module) so these fill",
    "without the Delta-t coincidence matcher, which needs gamma/thgem channels",
    "that are not defined on this setup. Served live over THttpServer:8090",
    "(browse with JSROOT). After editing, reload without restarting the DAQ:",
    "  curl http://localhost:8090/ReloadHists",
    "A 'channel' key on a histogram is a cut: keep only hits on that channel."
  ],
  "histograms": [
    { "name": "channels", "type": "TH1D",
      "title": "channel occupancy;channel;counts",
      "fill": "channel", "bins": 16, "min": 0, "max": 16 },

